==Translingual==

====Pronunciation====
/a/ short or long [[schwa]]: as the a in above or ago

===Letter===
'''अ''' (a)

# The first letter and first vowel of the [[Devanagari]] script.  Besides the initial position in a word, the letter is not written, instead it is assumed in the form of the consonant characters unless another vowel matra is used or a diacritic mark, the [[virama]], removes it.

===Transliteration===
*[[w:IAST|IAST]]: a or A
*[[w:ITRANS|ITRANS]]: a

